    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[XAMPP for MAC 多域名 多站点 多虚拟主机配置]]></title>
      <url>http://uiste.github.io/2016/07/23/XAMPP-for-MAC-%E5%A4%9A%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D-%E5%A4%9A%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9-%E5%A4%9A%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%BA%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>记录用 Mac 配置Xampp，需求是能同时运行多个站点，多个域名，目录自定义</p>
<h3 id="配置多域名"><a href="#配置多域名" class="headerlink" title="配置多域名"></a>配置多域名</h3><h4 id="编辑hosts文件，目录是-etc-hosts-打开bash操作，因为mac有权限限制，因此需要暂时获取root权限。"><a href="#编辑hosts文件，目录是-etc-hosts-打开bash操作，因为mac有权限限制，因此需要暂时获取root权限。" class="headerlink" title="编辑hosts文件，目录是/etc/hosts,打开bash操作，因为mac有权限限制，因此需要暂时获取root权限。"></a>编辑hosts文件，目录是/etc/hosts,打开bash操作，因为mac有权限限制，因此需要暂时获取root权限。</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ sudo nano /etc/hosts</div><div class="line">Password:</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="输入密码，密码不会显示占用的位数，在gnu-nano编辑器中进行修改-按control-X退出，按Y确认"><a href="#输入密码，密码不会显示占用的位数，在gnu-nano编辑器中进行修改-按control-X退出，按Y确认" class="headerlink" title="输入密码，密码不会显示占用的位数，在gnu nano编辑器中进行修改,按control + X退出，按Y确认"></a>输入密码，密码不会显示占用的位数，在gnu nano编辑器中进行修改,按control + X退出，按Y确认</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">  GNU nano 2.0.6              File: /etc/hosts                                  </div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">##</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Host Database</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># localhost is used to configure the loopback interface</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># when the system is booting.  Do not change this entry.</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">##</span></div><div class="line">127.0.0.1       localhost</div><div class="line">255.255.255.255 broadcasthost</div><div class="line">::1             localhost</div><div class="line">此处省略n行...</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">127.0.0.1       www.server.com</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">^G Get Help  ^O WriteOut  ^R Read File ^Y Prev Page ^K Cut Text  ^C Cur Pos</div><div class="line">^X Exit      ^J Justify   ^W Where Is  ^V Next Page ^U UnCut Text^T To Spell</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="修改xampp的配置文件"><a href="#修改xampp的配置文件" class="headerlink" title="修改xampp的配置文件"></a>修改xampp的配置文件</h3><h4 id="修改httpd-conf文件，目录是-Applications-XAMPP-xamppfiles-etc-httpd-conf-在终端里输入命令如下"><a href="#修改httpd-conf文件，目录是-Applications-XAMPP-xamppfiles-etc-httpd-conf-在终端里输入命令如下" class="headerlink" title="修改httpd.conf文件，目录是/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/etc/httpd.conf,在终端里输入命令如下"></a>修改httpd.conf文件，目录是/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/etc/httpd.conf,在终端里输入命令如下</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ sudo nano /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/etc/httpd.conf</div><div class="line">Password:</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="打开httpd-conf文件后，按ctrl＋W搜索-“httpd-vhosts-conf”，去掉前面的-注释符，确保引入了-vhosts-虚拟主机配置文件。"><a href="#打开httpd-conf文件后，按ctrl＋W搜索-“httpd-vhosts-conf”，去掉前面的-注释符，确保引入了-vhosts-虚拟主机配置文件。" class="headerlink" title="打开httpd.conf文件后，按ctrl＋W搜索 “httpd-vhosts.conf”，去掉前面的 # 注释符，确保引入了 vhosts 虚拟主机配置文件。"></a>打开httpd.conf文件后，按ctrl＋W搜索 “httpd-vhosts.conf”，去掉前面的 # 注释符，确保引入了 vhosts 虚拟主机配置文件。</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">Include etc/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="再在httpd-conf的最后面添加一段以下代码-退出保存"><a href="#再在httpd-conf的最后面添加一段以下代码-退出保存" class="headerlink" title="再在httpd.conf的最后面添加一段以下代码,退出保存"></a>再在httpd.conf的最后面添加一段以下代码,退出保存</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">#uiste added by 2016-07-23</div><div class="line">&lt;Directory &quot;/Users/uiste/Sites/project&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">        #Options Indexes FollowSymLinks ExecCGI Includes #don&apos;t permission see list</div><div class="line">        Options All</div><div class="line">        AllowOverride All</div><div class="line">        Order allow,deny</div><div class="line">        Allow from all</div><div class="line">&lt;/Directory&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>如果出现<strong>Access forbidden!</strong>注意前面已经进行设置是否冲突，或者尝试对站点文件夹进行权限设置<br>chmod -R 777 /Users/uiste/Sites/project</p>
</blockquote>
<h4 id="打开文件httpd-vhosts-conf文件，目录是-Applications-XAMPP-xamppfiles-etc-extra-httpd-vhosts-conf-在终端里输入命令如下："><a href="#打开文件httpd-vhosts-conf文件，目录是-Applications-XAMPP-xamppfiles-etc-extra-httpd-vhosts-conf-在终端里输入命令如下：" class="headerlink" title="打开文件httpd-vhosts.conf文件，目录是/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/etc/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf,在终端里输入命令如下："></a>打开文件httpd-vhosts.conf文件，目录是/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/etc/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf,在终端里输入命令如下：</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ sudo nano /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/etc/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>输入密码后打开httpd-vhosts.conf文件开始编辑<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;</div><div class="line">    ServerAdmin webmaster@server.com</div><div class="line">    DocumentRoot &quot;/Users/uiste/Sites/project/server/&quot;</div><div class="line">    ServerName www.server.com</div><div class="line">    ErrorLog &quot;logs/dummy-host3.example.com-error_log&quot;</div><div class="line">    CustomLog &quot;logs/dummy-host3.example.com-access_log&quot; common</div><div class="line">&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>编辑完成后，按ctrl＋X退出，按Y保存，重启xampp，浏览器输入127.0.0.1 www.server.com 页面出来会指向不同的站点。</p>
<h3 id="MySQL配置"><a href="#MySQL配置" class="headerlink" title="MySQL配置"></a>MySQL配置</h3><h4 id="找到config-inc-php文件-路径是-Applications-XAMPP-xamppfiles-phpmyadmin-config-inc-php"><a href="#找到config-inc-php文件-路径是-Applications-XAMPP-xamppfiles-phpmyadmin-config-inc-php" class="headerlink" title="找到config.inc.php文件,路径是/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/phpmyadmin/config.inc.php"></a>找到config.inc.php文件,路径是/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/phpmyadmin/config.inc.php</h4><p>在终端里输入命令如下：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ sudo nano /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/phpmyadmin/config.inc.php</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>打开文件config.inc.php后，找到$cfg[‘Servers’][$i][‘password’] = ‘’，改为$cfg[‘Servers’][$i][‘password’] = ‘123’; 保存退出后，重启xampp即可。</p>
<h4 id="终端进入mysql命令行操作"><a href="#终端进入mysql命令行操作" class="headerlink" title="终端进入mysql命令行操作"></a>终端进入mysql命令行操作</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/mysql</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr>
<p>###可视化文件配置方法</p>
<p>####开启虚拟主机配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">文件：/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/etc/httpd.conf</div><div class="line">配置： httpd-vhosts.conf</div><div class="line">    #取消#号开启虚拟主机</div><div class="line">    Include conf/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>####设置站点文件及访问权限<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">文件：httpd-vhosts.conf</div><div class="line">配置：</div><div class="line">    &lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;</div><div class="line">        ServerAdmin www.test.com</div><div class="line">        DocumentRoot &quot;/Users/uiste/www&quot;</div><div class="line">        ServerName www.test.com</div><div class="line">        #开启访问权限</div><div class="line">        &lt;Directory &quot;/Users/uiste/www&quot;&gt;         </div><div class="line">        Allow from all</div><div class="line">        &lt;/Directory&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>####DNS解析<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">文件：etc/hosts</div><div class="line">127.0.0.1   www.test.com</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
]]></content>
